wsintelliauction.lib.net
Interface NetworkManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientNetworkManager, ServerNetworkManager
public interface NetworkManager

Interface defining an application's network manager. A network manager must handle the creation and management of all sockets (and connection requests), as well as management of incoming and outgoing data messages.
